00:00:27.702 --> 00:00:30.160 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA MEREDITH: One of the
great frustrations many of us

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:32.610 align:middle line:10%
have is that we feel our
government representatives turn

00:00:32.610 --> 00:00:35.950 align:middle line:10%
a blind eye while Wall
Street robs us blind.

00:00:35.950 --> 00:00:37.870 align:middle line:84%
