fact, aware people

00:00:37.870 --> 00:00:39.890 align:middle line:84%
at the top of the
political spectrum who

00:00:39.890 --> 00:00:41.410 align:middle line:90%
are paying attention.

00:00:41.410 --> 00:00:44.120 align:middle line:84%
