00:32:03.020 --> 00:32:03.820 align:middle line:90%
>>HELLYER: Exactly.

00:32:03.820 --> 00:32:07.300 align:middle line:84%
And I'm so concerned
about these things.

00:32:07.300 --> 00:32:12.817 align:middle line:84%
I never carry pictures of my
children or my grandchildren.

00:32:12.817 --> 00:32:13.900 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Just chemtrails.

00:32:13.900 --> 00:32:17.530 align:middle line:84%
>>HELLYER: But I
carry a picture of

00:32:17.530 --> 00:32:22.160 align:middle line:84%
my little great-granddaughter
to remind me why I'm fighting.

00:32:22.160 --> 00:32:26.540 align:middle line:84%
Because the air she breathes,
the water she drinks,

00:32:26.540 --> 00:32:30.260 align:middle line:84%
and the soil where
her food will be grown

00:32:30.260 --> 00:32:33.890 align:middle line:84%
is all being
poisoned by somebody.

00:32:33.890 --> 00:32:35.050 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, it is.

00:32:35.050 --> 00:32:37.825 align:middle line:84%
>>HELLYER: And they don't
have my permission to do that.

00:32:37.825 --> 00:32:40.500 align:middle line:90%
And they don't have hers.

00:32:40.500 --> 00:32:42.560 align:middle line:90%
So where do they get it?

00:32:42.560 --> 00:32:44.030 align:middle line:90%
Where do they get the orders?

00:32:44.030 --> 00:32:45.750 align:middle line:90%
Who is responsible for it?

00:32:45.750 --> 00:32:47.305 align:middle line:90%
Who said they could do it?

00:32:47.305 --> 00:32:48.687 align:middle line:90%
And I think we should know that.

00:32:48.687 --> 00:32:49.520 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: We should.

00:32:49.520 --> 00:32:52.780 align:middle line:84%
Now we just have a
few minutes left.

00:32:52.780 --> 00:32:55.420 align:middle line:84%
Let's talk about the way
you see it lining up,

00:32:55.420 --> 00:32:57.304 align:middle line:90%
because it all comes back on us.

00:32:57.304 --> 00:32:59.095 align:middle line:84%
I mean, if we change
the banking structure,

00:32:59.095 --> 00:33:03.180 align:middle line:84%
it means that cheap
and easy credit may not

00:33:03.180 --> 00:33:05.800 align:middle line:84%
be available to us to go
buy a thousand-dollar purse

00:33:05.800 --> 00:33:08.580 align:middle line:84%
at the age of 15 that
you can't afford,

00:33:08.580 --> 00:33:10.850 align:middle line:84%
and you'll be paying
back for years and years.

00:33:10.850 --> 00:33:14.680 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we have been duped in to
the consumer consciousness that

00:33:14.680 --> 00:33:15.800 align:middle line:90%
feeds this.

00:33:15.800 --> 00:33:19.140 align:middle line:84%
So let's talk about it from a
personal responsibility level

00:33:19.140 --> 00:33:23.435 align:middle line:84%
forward, what we have to do
to start altering the system.

00:33:23.435 --> 00:33:25.920 align:middle line:84%
>>HELLYER: Well, we have
to understand leverage,

00:33:25.920 --> 00:33:28.320 align:middle line:84%
where we started out
this conversation.

00:33:28.320 --> 00:33:32.130 align:middle line:84%
I usually go back to the
time when the Bank of England

00:33:32.130 --> 00:33:38.530 align:middle line:84%
was chartered and the king was
fighting a war against France.

00:33:38.530 --> 00:33:41.140 align:middle line:84%
He needed some more money
to replenish his supplies

00:33:41.140 --> 00:33:42.880 align:middle line:84%
and build some new
ships and things.

00:33:42.880 --> 00:33:45.000 align:middle line:90%
His credit was no good.

00:33:45.000 --> 00:33:48.460 align:middle line:84%
So it was suggested
he start a bank.

00:33:48.460 --> 00:33:52.522 align:middle line:84%
And Parliament authorized
the Bank of England.

00:33:52.522 --> 00:33:57.360 align:middle line:84%
And rich people put in 1,200,000
pounds of gold and silver,

00:33:57.360 --> 00:34:00.092 align:middle line:84%
and lent it all to
the king at 8%, which

00:34:00.092 --> 00:34:02.550 align:middle line:84%
was a pretty high interest rate
for a government-guaranteed

00:34:02.550 --> 00:34:04.530 align:middle line:90%
loan.

00:34:04.530 --> 00:34:08.969 align:middle line:84%
So to show his appreciation,
the king said, well,

00:34:08.969 --> 00:34:14.989 align:middle line:84%
you can now print-- P-R-I-N-T--
$1,200,000 in bank notes

00:34:14.989 --> 00:34:17.699 align:middle line:84%
and lend them to your friends
at high interest rates.

00:34:17.699 --> 00:34:21.880 align:middle line:84%
So in effect, they were allowed
to lend the same money twice.

00:34:21.880 --> 00:34:22.710 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:34:22.710 --> 00:34:24.168 align:middle line:84%
>>HELLYER: Well,
in the early years

00:34:24.168 --> 00:34:27.040 align:middle line:84%
of the 20th century
in the United States,

00:34:27.040 --> 00:34:29.360 align:middle line:84%
your federally-chartered
banks had

00:34:29.360 --> 00:34:33.690 align:middle line:90%
to have gold reserves of 25%.

00:34:33.690 --> 00:34:38.260 align:middle line:84%
So they were allowed to lend
the same money four times.

00:34:38.260 --> 00:34:42.690 align:middle line:84%
In my country, Canada,
when I was younger,

00:34:42.690 --> 00:34:46.139 align:middle line:84%
the banks had to have
8% cash reserves.

00:34:46.139 --> 00:34:48.679 align:middle line:90%


00:34:48.679 --> 00:34:52.810 align:middle line:84%
Which meant they could lend
the same money 12.5 times.

00:34:52.810 --> 00:35:00.380 align:middle line:84%
In 1991, our government
took off that requirement.

00:35:00.380 --> 00:35:04.080 align:middle line:84%
And now they don't have
to have any cash reserve.

00:35:04.080 --> 00:35:05.950 align:middle line:84%
And when Milton
Friedman came along,

00:35:05.950 --> 00:35:10.580 align:middle line:84%
we changed the system from cash
reserves to capital reserves.

00:35:10.580 --> 00:35:13.460 align:middle line:84%
And the capital that
they have to have now,

00:35:13.460 --> 00:35:16.910 align:middle line:84%
as we've been
talking about, is 5%

00:35:16.910 --> 00:35:20.510 align:middle line:84%
in order to create a
dollar, or a pound,

00:35:20.510 --> 00:35:22.820 align:middle line:84%
or whatever it is
that's created.

00:35:22.820 --> 00:35:30.110 align:middle line:84%
And this system is
just so lopsided

00:35:30.110 --> 00:35:35.000 align:middle line:84%
because all of the people in the
world, other than the bankers,

00:35:35.000 --> 00:35:36.340 align:middle line:90%
can't do that.

00:35:36.340 --> 00:35:40.015 align:middle line:84%
I mean, you can't lend three
or four different people

00:35:40.015 --> 00:35:41.750 align:middle line:84%
the same money and
get away with it.

00:35:41.750 --> 00:35:42.550 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:35:42.550 --> 00:35:43.910 align:middle line:90%
>>HELLYER: But the banks can.

00:35:43.910 --> 00:35:45.580 align:middle line:90%
So we have to change the system.

00:35:45.580 --> 00:35:47.410 align:middle line:90%
We have to change the rules.

00:35:47.410 --> 00:35:49.810 align:middle line:84%
And that's the reason
that I'm suggesting

00:35:49.810 --> 00:35:53.000 align:middle line:84%
that we reduce the
leverage over seven years,

00:35:53.000 --> 00:35:56.516 align:middle line:84%
because we want to have
a smooth transition.

00:35:56.516 --> 00:35:58.970 align:middle line:84%
A lot of my colleagues
would do things faster.

00:35:58.970 --> 00:36:01.300 align:middle line:84%
And I said, hey, you're
going to disrupt markets.

00:36:01.300 --> 00:36:03.870 align:middle line:84%
You're going to do all
sorts of crazy things

00:36:03.870 --> 00:36:06.060 align:middle line:90%
that you can't perceive.

00:36:06.060 --> 00:36:08.760 align:middle line:84%
We'll do it over
an extended period,

00:36:08.760 --> 00:36:11.160 align:middle line:84%
and it'll be so smooth
that people will hardly

00:36:11.160 --> 00:36:12.240 align:middle line:90%
know that it's happening.

00:36:12.240 --> 00:36:17.570 align:middle line:84%
Except that these very rich
people who are promoting things

00:36:17.570 --> 00:36:21.230 align:middle line:84%
like the Trans-Pacific
Partnership,

00:36:21.230 --> 00:36:24.860 align:middle line:84%
which is nothing but the biggest
power grab in the history

00:36:24.860 --> 00:36:25.780 align:middle line:90%
of the world--

00:36:25.780 --> 00:36:28.570 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Please explain
it in encapsulation

00:36:28.570 --> 00:36:30.830 align:middle line:84%
form for us so we understand
what it is and why.

00:36:30.830 --> 00:36:32.330 align:middle line:84%
>>HELLYER: The
Trans-Pacific Partner

00:36:32.330 --> 00:36:35.580 align:middle line:84%
is the United States
and Canada and a lot

00:36:35.580 --> 00:36:40.390 align:middle line:84%
of countries around
the Pacific Rim

00:36:40.390 --> 00:36:45.370 align:middle line:84%
taking power from the people and
transferring it to the Cabal,

00:36:45.370 --> 00:36:50.140 align:middle line:84%
basically, to the banks and to
the transnational corporations,

00:36:50.140 --> 00:36:55.332 align:middle line:84%
and taking it away from their
legislatures and their courts.

00:36:55.332 --> 00:36:57.270 align:middle line:84%
And it should be a
criminal offense.

00:36:57.270 --> 00:36:58.450 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:36:58.450 --> 00:37:02.510 align:middle line:84%
>>HELLYER: And yet
it's almost done.

00:37:02.510 --> 00:37:06.104 align:middle line:90%
And this is really tragic.

00:37:06.104 --> 00:37:07.520 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And we
slept through it.

00:37:07.520 --> 00:37:08.686 align:middle line:90%
>>HELLYER: Slept through it.

00:37:08.686 --> 00:37:12.430 align:middle line:84%
We're just waiting for these
to be signed and sealed.

00:37:12.430 --> 00:37:18.430 align:middle line:84%
But these are the
culmination of globalization,

00:37:18.430 --> 00:37:22.770 align:middle line:84%
all in the direction of
a world government run by

00:37:22.770 --> 00:37:29.060 align:middle line:84%
and for the elite people and
the bankers of this world.

00:37:29.060 --> 00:37:34.960 align:middle line:84%
And they've been working
at it since the 1940s,

00:37:34.960 --> 00:37:37.550 align:middle line:90%
during the war period.

00:37:37.550 --> 00:37:40.360 align:middle line:84%
Before the war was
even over, the Council

00:37:40.360 --> 00:37:43.070 align:middle line:84%
on Foreign Relations said,
we're going to build an empire.

00:37:43.070 --> 00:37:48.320 align:middle line:84%
It's going to be bigger
than the German empire.

00:37:48.320 --> 00:37:53.320 align:middle line:84%
It's going to encompass those
lands, ours, all of America,

00:37:53.320 --> 00:37:54.365 align:middle line:90%
Pacific Rim--

00:37:54.365 --> 00:37:55.240 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Big vision.

00:37:55.240 --> 00:37:57.060 align:middle line:90%
>>HELLYER: Big fish.

00:37:57.060 --> 00:38:04.190 align:middle line:84%
And it's going to make this
empire look better and bigger

00:38:04.190 --> 00:38:08.390 align:middle line:84%
than any other empire in
the history of the world.

00:38:08.390 --> 00:38:09.540 align:middle line:90%
Wrong direction to go.

00:38:09.540 --> 00:38:11.290 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: As we were
talking about before,

00:38:11.290 --> 00:38:14.290 align:middle line:84%
is there a direct
line between what

00:38:14.290 --> 00:38:17.520 align:middle line:84%
happened in Roswell
those days, a direct line

00:38:17.520 --> 00:38:19.540 align:middle line:84%
through to the money
mafia that we know today?

00:38:19.540 --> 00:38:21.870 align:middle line:84%
>>HELLYER: I would say
there is a direct line, yes.

00:38:21.870 --> 00:38:29.330 align:middle line:84%
It's a cabal which, in effect,
has taken over responsibility

00:38:29.330 --> 00:38:32.360 align:middle line:90%
for the ET file.

00:38:32.360 --> 00:38:38.030 align:middle line:84%
And this cabal, as you know,
starts with the bankers,

00:38:38.030 --> 00:38:39.460 align:middle line:90%
the banking cartel.

00:38:39.460 --> 00:38:40.945 align:middle line:90%
That's the apex.

00:38:40.945 --> 00:38:45.750 align:middle line:84%
Then the oil cartel, and then
the transnational corporations

00:38:45.750 --> 00:38:50.250 align:middle line:84%
and the whole idea
of globalization,

00:38:50.250 --> 00:38:53.190 align:middle line:90%
then the intelligence agencies.

00:38:53.190 --> 00:38:57.226 align:middle line:84%
Many of them, but
especially the CIA,

00:38:57.226 --> 00:38:58.725 align:middle line:84%
are responsible for
a lot of things.

00:38:58.725 --> 00:39:05.670 align:middle line:84%
And the FBI and the
NSA and maybe the MI6

00:39:05.670 --> 00:39:08.960 align:middle line:84%
helps them a little bit, and
the Mossad from time to time.

00:39:08.960 --> 00:39:12.710 align:middle line:84%
And then a huge chunk of
the American military.

00:39:12.710 --> 00:39:14.810 align:middle line:90%
And they're all in it together.

00:39:14.810 --> 00:39:21.240 align:middle line:84%
But the line goes right up
to the top elite people,

00:39:21.240 --> 00:39:23.380 align:middle line:84%
and perhaps with
their connection

00:39:23.380 --> 00:39:27.170 align:middle line:84%
even with some secret societies
that we're not aware of.

00:39:27.170 --> 00:39:29.810 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So with our
few minutes remaining,

00:39:29.810 --> 00:39:35.170 align:middle line:84%
what can we, the people, do to
now get some integrity, dignity

00:39:35.170 --> 00:39:37.420 align:middle line:84%
back in our own lives,
to recover ourselves?

00:39:37.420 --> 00:39:41.290 align:middle line:84%
Let's just assume-- let's
say we have political means.

00:39:41.290 --> 00:39:42.870 align:middle line:84%
Maybe just quickly
delineate what

00:39:42.870 --> 00:39:45.820 align:middle line:84%
those are, what tools
we have at our disposal,

00:39:45.820 --> 00:39:47.720 align:middle line:84%
and then what we can
do personally now?

00:39:47.720 --> 00:39:49.880 align:middle line:84%
>>HELLYER: Well,
I've been preaching

00:39:49.880 --> 00:39:53.610 align:middle line:90%
for weeks and months and years.

00:39:53.610 --> 00:39:58.330 align:middle line:84%
If enough people put
pressure on politicians,

00:39:58.330 --> 00:40:00.690 align:middle line:90%
something would happen.

00:40:00.690 --> 00:40:03.165 align:middle line:84%
But there's only one thing
that politicians understand,

00:40:03.165 --> 00:40:05.980 align:middle line:90%
and that's pressure.

00:40:05.980 --> 00:40:09.090 align:middle line:84%
Are they going to
get reelected or not?

00:40:09.090 --> 00:40:12.690 align:middle line:84%
And if they think they're not,
they'll change their minds.

00:40:12.690 --> 00:40:13.490 align:middle line:90%
But as long--

00:40:13.490 --> 00:40:15.997 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Can they
legislate this problem away?

00:40:15.997 --> 00:40:18.580 align:middle line:84%
>>HELLYER: Well, they could drop
the Trans-Pacific Partnership

00:40:18.580 --> 00:40:20.730 align:middle line:84%
and say, we will not go
for that because it's

00:40:20.730 --> 00:40:23.370 align:middle line:90%
a violation of our constitution.

00:40:23.370 --> 00:40:25.520 align:middle line:84%
At least in our country,
it would unilaterally

00:40:25.520 --> 00:40:31.695 align:middle line:84%
change our constitution and take
away our basic banking rights.

00:40:31.695 --> 00:40:33.820 align:middle line:84%
And we would not be able
to do the things that I've

00:40:33.820 --> 00:40:36.620 align:middle line:90%
been proposing in my books.

00:40:36.620 --> 00:40:39.560 align:middle line:90%
And in my opinion, it's illegal.

00:40:39.560 --> 00:40:41.130 align:middle line:90%
It's immoral.

00:40:41.130 --> 00:40:44.400 align:middle line:84%
I don't know if the Supreme
Court would overrule it or not.

00:40:44.400 --> 00:40:46.270 align:middle line:84%
But certainly if
they go through,

00:40:46.270 --> 00:40:48.250 align:middle line:84%
we'll have to try and
get the Supreme Court

00:40:48.250 --> 00:40:49.940 align:middle line:90%
to take a look at it.

00:40:49.940 --> 00:40:57.460 align:middle line:84%
Because it just would be end of
the road for doing what we have

00:40:57.460 --> 00:41:04.760 align:middle line:84%
to do and should do in order
to set the world right for not

00:41:04.760 --> 00:41:07.440 align:middle line:84%
just great-granddaughters but
granddaughters and daughters

00:41:07.440 --> 00:41:08.240 align:middle line:90%
and--

00:41:08.240 --> 00:41:11.494 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So use our ability to
still apply political pressure.

00:41:11.494 --> 00:41:12.410 align:middle line:90%
>>HELLYER: Absolutely.

00:41:12.410 --> 00:41:15.520 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Then from
there, what do we do?

00:41:15.520 --> 00:41:19.350 align:middle line:84%
>>HELLYER: Well, that means we
have to change our priorities.

00:41:19.350 --> 00:41:21.750 align:middle line:84%
And even though
we're busy trying

00:41:21.750 --> 00:41:24.620 align:middle line:84%
to pay the next month's
rent and so on, say,

00:41:24.620 --> 00:41:29.400 align:middle line:84%
got to take a timeout to protect
my future rights as well.

00:41:29.400 --> 00:41:32.860 align:middle line:90%
So got to take an interest.

00:41:32.860 --> 00:41:36.225 align:middle line:84%
Because a lot of
people don't vote.

00:41:36.225 --> 00:41:39.640 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people don't
care about voting.

00:41:39.640 --> 00:41:43.680 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people
don't read anything

00:41:43.680 --> 00:41:47.810 align:middle line:84%
on the subject that's
more substantial than they

00:41:47.810 --> 00:41:54.870 align:middle line:84%
get in the controlled press,
or listen to anything that's

00:41:54.870 --> 00:41:56.965 align:middle line:90%
contrary to the news reports.

00:41:56.965 --> 00:41:58.160 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That's true.

00:41:58.160 --> 00:42:01.450 align:middle line:84%
>>HELLYER: And individual
responsibility.

00:42:01.450 --> 00:42:04.250 align:middle line:84%
I remember Paul
Herr saying that.

00:42:04.250 --> 00:42:07.990 align:middle line:84%
Individual responsibility
is what we have to take.

00:42:07.990 --> 00:42:10.260 align:middle line:90%
We have to change our own lives.

00:42:10.260 --> 00:42:12.540 align:middle line:84%
And we have to
take responsibility

00:42:12.540 --> 00:42:15.302 align:middle line:84%
for changing the system for
the benefit of other people.

00:42:15.302 --> 00:42:17.870 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And do you
believe we can do that?

00:42:17.870 --> 00:42:19.220 align:middle line:90%
>>HELLYER: Theoretically, yes.

00:42:19.220 --> 00:42:24.520 align:middle line:84%
Theoretically, I
believe in miracles.

00:42:24.520 --> 00:42:26.770 align:middle line:90%
I am not an oddsmaker.

00:42:26.770 --> 00:42:30.980 align:middle line:84%
The odds are so far against
us because of the power,

00:42:30.980 --> 00:42:38.160 align:middle line:84%
especially of the bankers and
the transnational corporations.

00:42:38.160 --> 00:42:45.030 align:middle line:10%
But as Yogi Berra said, it's
not over till it's over.

00:42:45.030 --> 00:42:48.180 align:middle line:10%
So we got to keep
fighting and doing

00:42:48.180 --> 00:42:52.370 align:middle line:10%
everything we can to see
if we can't get that home

00:42:52.370 --> 00:42:56.860 align:middle line:10%
run, the loaded bases at
the end of the innings,

00:42:56.860 --> 00:42:59.587 align:middle line:10%
and stop this nonsense
before it's too late.

00:42:59.587 --> 00:43:01.420 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Paul, I want
to thank you so much.

00:43:01.420 --> 00:43:03.310 align:middle line:84%
And again, people can
read "The Money Mafia."

00:43:03.310 --> 00:43:06.590 align:middle line:84%
And it'll give the diagram of
how all of this came to be,

00:43:06.590 --> 00:43:08.810 align:middle line:84%
and again, your action
plan at the end.

00:43:08.810 --> 00:43:11.400 align:middle line:84%
And I thank you so much
for all the public service

00:43:11.400 --> 00:43:14.090 align:middle line:84%
and the careful thought
and consideration.

00:43:14.090 --> 00:43:18.000 align:middle line:84%
And once again, as you say,
a return to basic morality

00:43:18.000 --> 00:43:19.464 align:middle line:90%
is what we need.

00:43:19.464 --> 00:43:20.630 align:middle line:90%
>>HELLYER: It's my pleasure.

00:43:20.630 --> 00:43:24.540 align:middle line:84%
And thank you for giving me
the opportunity to sound off.

